bcl:definition.bcl:text:
affiliated corporation has the same meaning as "affiliate" in
  section 1
  (1) of the Business Corporations Act;

captive insurance company means a company that is a pure
captive insurance company, an association captive insurance company or a sophisticated
insured captive insurance company;

bcl:paragraph.bcl:text:
the application, in respect of a captive insurance company or a class of captive
            insurance companies, of provisions of the Insurance
                Act;
